# Amazon Short URL

A script to shorten Amazon product page URLs.

## Usage

```zsh
amazon-short-url [url-of-product-page]
```

## Installation

With `pipx`:

```zsh
pipx install amazon-short-url
```

With `pip`:

```zsh
pip install amazon-short-url
```

